Business Brief -- Allied Research Corp.:
   Net Rose 45% in 4th Period
   While Revenue Quadrupled
For the year, the company reported net of $14.2 million,
or $3.38 a share, up from $23,000, or one cent a share.
Revenue shot up to $174.7 million from $51.2 million.
   Allied Research's shares closed at $12.50, up $1 in
national over-the-counter trading.